<plot>In Black Men and Me, a woman explores her position as a Trinidadian lesbian and her complex relationship with black men. Shot in a barbershop, a traditional gathering place for black men, she has her head shaved while she reflects on her black masculinity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?073267</url></doc>
